reviewText: I RECEIVED MY MERCHANDISE AND IT DID NOT WORK PROPERLY. WHEN I ATTEMPTED TO WATCH THE VHS TAPE IT WAS DEFECTIVE AND DID NOT WORK. I TRIED EVERYTHING WITH NO SUCCESS.

An action packed film, with some unique and innovative martial arts styles, along with a complex story line.  A cart driver gets mixed up with  an assassin, and  then get's in the middle of a group of thugs, and there  hope to get a large ammount of money. But it seems as though every thing  that turns bad, happens to go through one man.  And the attempt to end his  life ends up turning into a massive fight sequence leading to a  whole lot  a death, and a very surprising ending.
